Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue-nosed Reindeer!\NChopper's Secret"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow... and you're\Nnot completely hiding, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh... Shut up, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, how's your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fever seems to have\Ncome down a little, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,38.2 degrees... Hmm...\NYou're doing more or less all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor. Dr. Kureha.\NCall me Doctorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... Then I'm in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My secret to staying young?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. You're in the\Ncastle on top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there were two others\Nbesides me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're sleeping in the next room...\Nvery deeply. What tough guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were bitten by a bug called Kestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a poisonous tick that lives in jungles\Nwith high temperature and humidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're bitten by it,\Nbacteria come in and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,keep you in pain by lying dormant\Ninside your body for 5 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It causes high fever of above 40 degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coinfection, myocarditis,\Narteritis, cerebritis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the infection's progression\Nfrom the bitten area,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you've been\Ninfected for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suffering must've\Nbeen unusually harsh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it would've eased up in 2 more\Ndays even without any treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 2 more days...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because you\Nwould've died in 2 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the "5-day disease."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kestia died\Nout 100 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was useful that I kept\Nthe antibiotic just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you guys come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you out walking around\Nwith your belly exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a jungle on an ancient\Nisland or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's just silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:05:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ring a bell? What a crazy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in bed. Your treatment\Nhasn't completely finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. So long as my\Nfever comes down, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body will take care of\Nitself after that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This disease normally takes at\Nleast 10 days to fully treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you want to\Nsuffer some more and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with my medicine,\Nyou'll have to rest at least 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't stay here for 3 days!\NWe have to take Vivi to Alabasta soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a patient of mine leaves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's either cured or dead.\NI won't let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He climbed this mountain\Nwith his bare hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This 5000m high Drum Rock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His entire body is nearly frostbitten.\NWhat was he thinking dressing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat water immediately\Nand throw him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's bleeding badly.\N6 broken ribs and a spinal fissure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I operate on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the most critical\None is this girl. She's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Have phenicol,\Ncardiotonic and tialcillin ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have an infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The pathogen\Nisn't from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll make both that\Nbleeding kid and this girl all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my friends...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the picture. I'll save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Let's begin treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my friends...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venison stew needs to be\Ncooked in a pot for 3 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the meat becomes properly tender...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venison...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! I'll cook this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! I'll make a nutritious\Nvenison dish for Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised!\NThey can already move around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that talking stuffed\Ndeer with a blue nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asking me what he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! I'm telling you\Nnot to eat it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Chopper.\NHe's just a reindeer with a blue nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeers don't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-stop it, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's different from\Nordinary reindeers in some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's different...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just because he ate a\NHuman Human Fruit. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Human Human Fruit...\NOne of the devil fruits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He's a reindeer who\Ngained the humans' abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats! Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:10:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I taught him everything\NI know about medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol-sama.\NThat Straw Hat is up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat the rubber man for a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find him in time, for sure!\NBe alive, Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there! Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't just\Nstand there and help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found him! We found Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They found him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become one of my crew!\NPlease, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need a doctor on our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... You said that's your name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "old lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did, old la...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch... what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the youthful 130s.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... What an incredible old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to be a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!\NIt'll be a waste of my glorious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Let's go on\Nan adventure, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey. I just told you to\Nwatch what you say, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Wait, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Nami-san!\NI'll cook a nutritious reindeer dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I'll eat you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did she come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming! She's coming!\NShe's coming! She's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the food.\NI just want some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...? Even though\Nthis is inside the castle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I should close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay in bed!\N--I should close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. It seems like\Nit's pretty much gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I lost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Doctorine's medicine works well,\Nthe fever goes away quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kestia's bacteria\Nstill remain in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the antibiotic shot\Nand stay in bed, or you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been attending me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be thanked by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type that\Ncan't hide their emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This castle is strange.\NIt's cold and there's snow inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you before, you're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow everywhere in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doors for the unused\Nrooms are all frozen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, Luffy! Give up on\Nasking that old hag to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a doctor!\NShe's trying to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-real ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a flag with a skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's attached to our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You idiot! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Then... wanna come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the sea! Why don't you\Ncome with us...? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, that'll help me a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have a doctor on our ship,\NI won't have to stay here for 3 days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, on our ship, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Don't be ridiculous!\NI'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can stay with humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, don't you\Nget scared when you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer, but I stand on\Ntwo legs and I even speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you trying to scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is blue, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats sure are quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it... girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tempting the reindeer without\Nmy permission while I'm not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Do I need permission\Nto make a move on a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't. If you wanna\Ntake him, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be easy.\NHe has a scar in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big scar that\Neven I can't cure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment he was born into this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his group and even his\Nparents abandoned him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he had a blue nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always walked at the very back\Nof the group all by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though he was a new-born child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one day, he ate a devil\Nfruit and was treated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a monster even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reindeers fiercely\Npressured him to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was no longer an ordinary\Nreindeer in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he wanted friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he went down to a village,\Nas a human this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what's that creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his figure wasn't\Nexactly human, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason,\Nhis nose stayed blue, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a yeti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!\NGet the children inside quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun! Bring me a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't know what was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor did he know what to blame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just wanted friends,\Nyet he was called a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was no longer a reindeer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't a human, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lived all alone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys heal the scar in his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy. Look at that door at\Nthe front entrance. It's wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's close this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it open like this, there's no difference\Nbetween outside and inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it! Don't touch that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind what he says.\NLet's close it, or we'll freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:20:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Didn't I tell you to... stop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him? Why is he angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy. Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're baby snowbirds.\NWell, if we close the door, they'll fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they can't close it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wasn't he speaking earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:21:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come to think of it, I sort of\Nremember him standing on two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What the heck is that?\NHe's walking on two legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a reindeer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's short...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He becomes big...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cool guy! He's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Let's have him join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Did you see the reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys! Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that we're\Nnot trying to eat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper has had lots of\Nhardships in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that there was\None person who accepted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What kind of person was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Outcast's Dream!\NHiriluk the Quack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
